Typical scenarios when ajax is not working:

1) You are testing on local file, opening it directly in the browser. Due to browser security policies, your file has to be served through web server;

2) Your link is incorrect;

3) Your ajax request is blocked due to `same-origin policy`, see https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/CORS

Anyway, check console output (hit F12 to open developer tools), there should be a hint about what causes your issue.

